status reporter), while most of the other tasks have finished, failed, or been killed. Looking at the session statuses, most are done or failed, with only the three cron jobs running actively. The main session ended earlier as expected, and the 5p QLHV monitor is still going after about 35 minutes. Looking at the timestamps, cron:e7885813 hasn't updated since 20:03 UTC, which is a significant gap compared to the other sessions still actively running. The telegram:group session hasn't received new messages since 20:29 UTC, but it did get the report delivered, so it's still technically alive even if it's not actively being used right now.\\n\\nChecking against the baseline from 20:29 UTC, the pipeline is stable—no new sessions have spawned, no existing ones have died, and there are no failures or blockers to report. Everything appears to be running as expected, so there's nothing that needs to be flagged.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Silent. No state changes since last baseline (20:29 UTC).\\n\\n**Current stable sessions confirmed:**\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running (~35 min, updated 21:01 UTC)\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running (updated 20:56 UTC)\\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running (updated 20:03 UTC — stale but alive)\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ running (updated 20:29 UTC)\\n\\nPipeline: HEALTHY. Blockers: none.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 20128,\n            \"output\": 693,\n            \"totalTokens\": 35181,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 416,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776200545927,\n          \"responseId\": \"062dde63a0568fa0da6d268700037b24\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n 